# E-Commerce Backend (Spring Boot)

## Features
- User Authentication (Register/Login)
- Product Management
- Cart Management
- Order Processing

## Tech Stack
- Spring Boot
- MySQL
- JPA/Hibernate

## How to Run
1. Create database: ecommerce_db
2. Update application.properties
3. Run project:
   mvn spring-boot:run

## API Endpoints
POST /auth/register  
POST /auth/login  
GET /products  